mySNAdata <- read.csv("/Users/luke/Documents/HUDK4050/ACA4/ACA4_Data.csv", row.names = 1)

mynet <- graph_from_adjacency_matrix(as.matrix(mySNAdata), weighted=TRUE, mode="undirected")

plot(mynet) 

vcount(mynet)
## [1] 10
ecount(mynet)
## [1] 38
#number of edges is 38 and nodes are 10


edge_density(mynet)
## [1] 0.8444444
#density is 0.84


diameter(mynet)
## [1] 2
#diameter is 2

degree(mynet)
##    LUKE      KX   YUJUN  HAIZHE  QIUHAN ANTHONY    ECHO     TOM   PETER    CHEN 
##       9       9       8       8       8       8       8       8       8       2
#degree centrality shows above

betweenness(mynet, directed = FALSE, normalized = TRUE)
##       LUKE         KX      YUJUN     HAIZHE     QIUHAN    ANTHONY       ECHO 
## 0.09722222 0.09722222 0.00000000 0.00000000 0.00000000 0.00000000 0.00000000 
##        TOM      PETER       CHEN 
## 0.00000000 0.00000000 0.00000000
#luke and kx have higher influence

fc <- cluster_fast_greedy(mynet)
membership(fc)
##    LUKE      KX   YUJUN  HAIZHE  QIUHAN ANTHONY    ECHO     TOM   PETER    CHEN 
##       2       2       1       1       1       1       1       1       1       2
sizes(fc)
## Community sizes
## 1 2 
## 7 3
#community 1 has 7 actors and community 2 has 3 actors


V(mynet)$color <- fc$membership
plot(mynet)
